title: Ep: 004 - Architect Caleb Johnson // The Human Experience
description: In our fourth episode of Architecture, Design, & Photography we sit down with Caleb Johnson, Principal Architect at Caleb Johnson Studio. We briefly discuss our past working history, the three categories that influence a design, and the human experience as it relates to architecture.
author: info@trentbell.com (Trent Bell)
